casebody.data:
Wednesday, November 15, 2000

MOTION DOCKET

00-1921. Pfahler v. Natl. Latex Prod. Co.

Ashland App. No. 00COA01380. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of the October 18, 2000 court of appeals judgment entry.

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay of court of appeals judgment entry be, and hereby is, denied.

Lundberg Stratton, J., dissents.
